without bothering anyone
or being bothered.

671
01:02:11,352 --> 01:02:15,523
Finding a place
where no one would reject me.

672
01:02:16,232 --> 01:02:20,528
That's what I thought living was.

673
01:02:21,487 --> 01:02:25,533
But now, I've changed my mind.

674
01:02:26,451 --> 01:02:30,538
Wherever it may be, my place can be
the place where I am right now.

675
01:02:31,581 --> 01:02:35,626
As long as I live as my true self,

676
01:02:36,627 --> 01:02:40,673
